{"tid":2398244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★調查指 專上學歷人士失業率高達8.9%，超越低學歷者！","createTime":"2021-02-07T06:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T04:38:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"710a2d8c74df34085b0f7764435ed49bb801578b","tid":2398244,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"社聯總主任黃和平指，受影響行業不限於基層職業，部分中等薪金職業的失業率亦高企。從事服務工作及銷售人員的失業率高達10.4%。失業情況亦不限於低學歷人士，具專上教育文憑學歷人士失業率高達8.9%，不時超越低學歷者。<br />\n<br />\n社聯總監黃健偉指，中或高等職位的人士一旦失業會較難找工作，失業時期中位數會較長，平均超過120日。他們的收入下跌驚人，家庭收入減幅平均超過5成。<br />\n<br />\n社聯指，失業及就業不足人士的貧窮率高，但只有約5%人士領取綜援，認為制度不能保障失業人士。他們建議政府研究失業保險制度，及進一步放寬職津計劃，下調最低工時要求到36小時等，又認為政府應設立短期失業援助金，協助基層市民解決燃眉之急。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574569-20210207.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574569-20210207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=81f40103\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574569-20210207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9561a962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574569-20210207.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a3153050387ac14884ec61820dcbdcbc5043bc9a","tid":2398244,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ff9af36577dfe39115c7129891310ecb169e34","tid":2398244,"uid":121580,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:34:05.000Z","msg":"sales